===Etymology===
Middle English [[maieste]], [[mageste]], from Old French [[majesté]], from Latin [[maiestas|māiestās]], derived from Proto-Indo-European ''*maǵ-yos-'' "greater", from ''*maǵ-, *meǵ-'' "great".

